file.name: any-of-anon-property-level.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: unit test
  version: 0.0.1
components:
  schemas:
    employee:
      properties:
        role:
          anyOf: 
          - type: object
            properties:
              employeeType:
                type: string 
                enum: ['Nurse']
              level:
                type: integer
            required:
            - level
          - type: object
            properties:
              employeeType:
                type: string 
                enum: ['Doctor']
              income:
                type: number
            required:
            - income
